title: Gold Lacquer Watchface
summary: This is a Premium watchface works on Android Wear device.
developerAddress: 神奈川県川崎市川崎区日進町
description: Gold Lacquer watch face is luxury watch face inspired by Japanese traditional. Works for both round and square watch. Please try it on if you have no time to design your cool watch face by using Facer Watch Face, WatchMaker Watch Face and so on. [How to set the watch face]When you install this app to your handheld device, you can find this watch face in your wearable device.[Update] - Support Android 5.0 Lollipop.
descriptionHTML:
Gold Lacquer watch face is luxury watch face inspired by Japanese traditional. Works for both round and square watch. Please try it on if you have no time to design your cool watch face by using Facer Watch Face, WatchMaker Watch Face and so on.

[How to set the watch face]
When you install this app to your handheld device, you can find this watch face in your wearable device.

[Update]
- Support Android 5.0 Lollipop.
